Makro has launched its Big Bang Sale, offering discounts of up to 30% off on selected hi-tech, multimedia, photographic, and cellular products. The sale runs from 30 April to 3 May and offers specials on a range of appliances and technology brands which are available in-store and online. Some of the specials include discounts on televisions and home entertainment products. Computer and gaming enthusiasts can also save big on gaming consoles and high-end laptops. For more details about the sale, click here: Makro Big Bang Sale (See the full catalogue here) <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-304642" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Samsung-QLED.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="427" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Samsung-QLED.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Samsung-QLED-600x400.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-304612" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Hisense.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="427" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Hisense.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Hisense-600x400.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-304614" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/HP.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="427" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/HP.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/HP-600x400.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-304646" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploa